<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mạdmt fy sfynty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- mạdmt fy sfynty rby ạ̉nạ mrtạḥ
 ạ̉nt ʿạlm ktr ạlạ̉mwạj fạnthr ạlryạḥ
 1- ạ̹n hạj ạlbḥr wạlạ̉mwạj llṭm ạlsfynẗ
 mạdạm mạsk ạldfẗ yswʿ trsy̱ ʿly̱ ạlmynạ
 2- ly ậlạm wḍyqạt hnạ fy gẖrbty
 fʿn qryb yạ̉ty yswʿ wysmḥ ạldmwʿ
 3- ạ̹n srt fy wạdy ạlbkạ ạ̉ṣyrh ynbwʿ
 fʿn qryb yạ̉ty yswʿ wymsḥ ạldmwʿ
 4- ldẖạ ạ̉ʿysẖ sẖạkraⁿạ dwmaⁿạ fy kl ḥyn
 wmhmạ hạjb ạlạ̉mwạj yswʿ ly mʿyn</lyrics>
